= Deploying new versions of the server =

To deploy your local version onto www.hoccer.com you can simply type 

 $ rake deploy
 
 
= Server Setup =

The server has a post-receive hook (.git/hooks/post-receive) to update the
server automaticly after :

--------------8<-----------
#!/bin/sh

unset GIT_DIR
PROJECT_DIR=`pwd`/../

cd $PROJECT_DIR
git reset --hard

rake db:migrate

touch tmp/restart.txt
-------------->8-----------

